data.description: WELCOME HOME TO THE COUNTRY!  This unique property boasts 8.02 acres just outside of the Crockett city limits.  You will enjoy the private atmosphere as you sit on your front or back porch, or even as you hunt your land!  With a recent addition to the home, there is now a handicap-accessible bedroom and bathroom combo downstairs which would be perfect for an extra guest suite.  There are also several outbuildings, including an insulated, cooled building which could be used for a guest house or workshop, a 2-car carport, 3-stall barn, and an additional storage shed.  The entire property is fenced with gated entrances off FM 2110 and CR 3550.  Some of the newest features include a recently upgraded on-site well, a new aerobic septic system, and upgraded windows throughout almost all of the house. Call or text to see this beautiful property today!
